亞思想<br />\n<br />\n係儒家思想 儒家死全家<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講印度 會有人咁要求明星"},{"pid":"df629038db43bed84983e35809a30f327ccd3907","tid":129379,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鄭中基一定紅 但佢唔檢點</blockquote><br />\n亞洲人思想 明星一定要好好形象 唔至香港 中日韓台都係咁 明星食煙叫雞都要比人公審</blockquote><br />\n唔係亞洲思想 係東亞思想<br />\n<br />\n係儒家思想 儒家死全家<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講印度 會有人咁要求明星</blockquote><br />\n外國都講形象既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無咁重視姐"},{"pid":"21f2cd821047f0922847f899a06d7e5cbeabac5c","tid":129379,"uid":7285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最接近果個咪鄭中基囉<br />\n唱到邊紅到邊</blockquote><br />\n鄭中基唔係發癲佢一定紅到今日。佢果陣紅到過台灣，講緊係好紅好紅，因為張學友帶佢出黎，再加上把超靚聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學友接班人根本係佢 唔係Eason</blockquote><br />\n同學友一齊拜師架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係一齊，係張學友先。<br />\n<br />\n當時歐丁玉同張學友去美國幫過敏世界大碟錄音。<br />\n仲係美國讀緊書嘅鄭中基去幫手。<br />\n咁啱啲和音甩晒底，歐丁玉就搵埋鄭中基一齊頂上。<br />\n唱完之後，歐丁玉話&quot;𡃁仔，你都幾唱得喎&quot;，就鼓勵佢錄demo。<br />\n<br />\n所以你聽張學友過敏世界，會聽到鄭中基把聲。<br />\n<br />\n之後先有鄭東漢就打本畀台灣金牌製作人周治平開公司幫鄭中基出道。<br />\n由96年到99年，周治平賺到每日數錢咁濟。<br />\n97-98年，鄭中基台灣唱片銷量仲高過劉德華，同張學友，張惠妹並列十大唱片。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係多醜聞，鄭中基可能會紅，但另一面如果佢冇反省，今日佢都未必儲到咁人氣。"},{"pid":"db5ef4c6e6a42adbc1aa0aed625d6b06e754e3f9","tid":129379,"uid":18781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:31:03.000Z","msg":"最有印象反而係呢首<br />\n生活靜靜似是湖水 全為你泛起生氣<br />\n全為你泛起了漣漪 歡笑全為你起"},{"pid":"e4fac46a26c6953f6f8497fe6d23ca6be3f29ef0","tid":129379,"uid":63618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"檸檬同鄭中基退出樂壇前咁撚紅都比人話無得同eason 比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64c3e9dc5d0ec1825bffe69cdde0032940f9ce7","tid":129379,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>檸檬同鄭中基退出樂壇前咁撚紅都比人話無得同eason 比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee5945ea2b09548cdf3072f76bd463cde9792a3","tid":129379,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>檸檬同鄭中基退出樂壇前咁撚紅都比人話無得同eason 比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係作兩個退 eason 邊有位上..<br />\n<br />\nbtw 咁多個最唱得肯定係暴龍哥"},{"pid":"326794c1bb0f3a873c7d5f8fd76c9496ae3ae5ba","tid":129379,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>檸檬同鄭中基退出樂壇前咁撚紅都比人話無得同eason 比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n特別係檸檬<br />\n當年佢紅到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc374958923b28102cc9d5e2300da17914a41cd0","tid":129379,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:36:09.000Z","msg":"最紅一定係檸檬同單春<br />\n咩鄭中基 陳曉東算吧啦<br />\n紅歌唔紅人"}]}